Custom Configuration Framework (custom-conf)
============================================
Package: custom-conf-php70-fpm

This package provides standard configuration of the PHP: Hypertext Processor
(version 7.0) along the FastCGI Process Manager (FPM).

In particular, it addresses standard configuration of:
 - Apache2 integration provisioning (<-> 'custom-conf-php70-apache2' package)
 - default settings hardening (php.ini)

